# 🐭 Whack-A-Mole

A fun browser-based Whack-A-Mole game built with vanilla HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

🎮 **[Play Live →](https://manyagkarle13.github.io/whack-a-mole/)**

## How to Play
- A mole and a bomb pop up randomly across 9 holes
- **Click the mole** to score points
- **Avoid the bomb** — hitting it costs you a life
- You have 3 lives and 30 seconds — get the highest score!

## Features
- Smooth mole animations
- Sound effects (Web Audio API — no files needed)
- Lives system with bomb penalty
- Speed increases as your score grows
- Works in any modern browser

## Tech Stack
- HTML5
- CSS3
- Vanilla JavaScript (no libraries)

## Run Locally
```bash
git clone https://github.com/manyagkarle13/whack-a-mole.git
cd whack-a-mole
# Just open index.html in your browser!
```

